    "They proposed a deep Q-learning-based algorithm to deal with this nonlinear integer programming problem.",
    "Interference mitigationDue to the shared resource and hardware, the ISAC may suffer from the significant inter-functionality interference between communication and sensing [239].",
    "The traditional interference mitigation algorithms may not be suitable for the large-scale optimization problems in ISAC networks due to their prohibitive computational complexity.",
    "AI techniques are expected to make interference mitigation more intelligent and effective due to the powerful learning capability and low complexity [240].",
    "AI-enabled interference mitigation for uplink ISAC is illustrated in Figure 16, where the ISAC BS simultaneously receives the echos reflected from the targets and the uplink communication signal from the users."
